{"tid":882910,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"孔乙己 之恆大升格","createTime":"2018-10-30T12:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T07:58:59.000Z","uid":200521,"like":117,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c30b42d77ebf9f4e68c9139534361454424ee45c","tid":882910,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:15:32.000Z","msg":"恆大仔一到店，所有便利店員便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「含大仔，你臉上又添上新的梅毒瘤了！」他不回答，對櫃裏說，「要盒幼卡碧，要一盒杜蕾斯。」便排出中銀恆大信用卡。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又偷拍人家裙底拿去賣錢了！」恆大仔睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空汚人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你偷拍林鄭葉私煙劉裙底，一邊打J。」恆大仔便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「竊春光不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;竊春光！&hellip;&hellip;大學生的事，能算偷麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「香港一大」，什麼「升格」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"4d139ec576c28ac24556d4421e6c243c71d8ecc9","tid":882910,"uid":198998,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:25:23.000Z","msg":"9.5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6039d4b543ccf90f510d1c79bfac9611f3860015","tid":882910,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"Yeah"},{"pid":"4d5c761846101b233a4a595cbfb1a71f2f0746d0","tid":882910,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d139ec576c28ac24556d4421e6c243c71d8ecc9","tid":882910,"uid":198998,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:25:23.000Z","msg":"9.5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"嗰0.5<br />\n分係送畀偉大嘅含大嘅"},{"pid":"592c8bcc77f4a62d3af32d9432e8c8f4ee0584be","tid":882910,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6039d4b543ccf90f510d1c79bfac9611f3860015","tid":882910,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"Yeah"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T13:54:04.000Z","msg":"你個名終於大派用場"},{"pid":"a151cce307640bd1bcfbce1b4b1f1d1689b50748","tid":882910,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re